Actions.Text: REFERRED TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS

Title: Exempts domestic and imported animals harvested at a game hunting preserve from the sales and compensating use tax
Summary: Exempts domestic and imported animals harvested at a game hunting preserve from the sales and compensating use tax.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the tax law, in relation to exempting domestic and imported game animals harvested at a game hunting preserve from the sales and compensating use tax
